	h3 Installation
	.codeblock $ npm install gzippo
	br
	h3 Usage
	br
	p In your express/connect server setup, use as follows:
	.codeblock
		| var gzippo = require('gzippo');
		br
		| //Replace the static provider with gzippo's
		br
		| //app.use(express.static(__dirname + '/public'));
		br
		| app.use(gzippo.staticGzip(__dirname + '/public'));
	br
	h3 Options
	br
	p matchType - A regular expression tested against the Content-Type header to determine whether the response should be gzipped or not. The default value is /text|javascript|json/.
	br
	p maxAge - cache-control max-age directive, defaulting to 1 day
